dct_title_s: International travel maps, Guatemala, scale 1:500,000: indexed
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Map continued on verso. Map shows international and departmental boundaries, principal archaeological sites and biosphere reserves. Includes list of abbreviations and geographic equivalents, index, and publisher's index map with listing. Ancillary map on recto: Antigua. On verso: Ciudad de Guatemala (Guatemala City) -- Environs of Guatemala City -- Tikal, Petén -- Quiriguá, Izabal -- Zaculeu, Huehuetenango.
